{
  "texts": [
    "This request acts as a mutation of the original M 2 and is inserted into the message sequence M ′, which is then sent to the server.Let us reconsider the RTSP example.",
    "Initially, the server is in the INIT state.",
    "Upon receiving the message sequence M 1 = {SETUP}, it responds with R 1 = {200-OK}, transitioning to the READY state.",
    "Subsequently, the fuzzer encounters a coverage plateau, where it fails to generate interesting seeds.",
    "Upon noticing this, we stimulate the LLM by presenting the communication history H = {SETUP, 200-OK}."
  ]
}